          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", which he has had in his possession for a decade now. We’re guessing the first owner didn’t have the vision of slamming this thing to the ground and making the other mods, but the end result sure is impressive.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
